website_content.title: Senior React Developer
website_content.markdown_content:
## Job Description

We are seeking a talented Senior React Developer to join our team.

### Responsibilities
- Build efficient and reusable front-end abstractions and systems
- Identify and address performance bottlenecks
- Participate in design and code reviews

### Requirements
- 5+ years of experience with JavaScript/TypeScript
- Deep understanding of React and its core principles
- Experience with modern front-end build pipelines and tools

website_content.title: WBHRB Staff Nurse Scorecard 2026
website_content.markdown_content:
## WBHRB Staff Nurse Scorecard 2026 Released!

The West Bengal Health Recruitment Board (WBHRB) has released the Candidate Response & Score Cards for the Staff Nurse Grade II posts on **February 16, 2026**. Candidates who appeared in the Computer Based Test (CBT) held on **December 31, 2025 & January 1, 2026** can now view their marks and response sheets online.

**Key Details:**
*   **Recruiting Body:** West Bengal Health Recruitment Board (WBHRB)
*   **Post Name:** Staff Nurse Grade II (GNM / Basic B.Sc. / Post Basic B.Sc.)
*   **Result Type:** Candidate Response & Score Card / Panel List
*   **Release Date:** February 16, 2026
*   **Selection Stages:** CBT → Interview (GNM) → Document Verification / Panel (B.Sc.)

**Scorecard Contains:**
*   Registration Number / Roll Number
*   Candidate Name
*   Category
*   Raw Marks (out of 100)
*   Pro-rated Raw Marks (out of 85)
*   Normalized Marks
*   Minimum Marks by last shortlisted candidate (category-wise)
*   Qualifying / Shortlist / Panel Status

**Important Instructions:**
*   Download and save your scorecard immediately.
*   Check the official website for interview schedules (GNM) or appointment details (B.Sc.).
*   Verify personal and marks details and report any discrepancies.
